Air Berlin Hires Cassani, Hammad as New Managers, FTD Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-10T14:50:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/air-berlin-hires-cassani-hammad-as-new-managers-ftd-reports.html
Air Berlin Plc (AB1)  appointed Barbara Cassani and Saad Hammad as new top managers to help it return to
profit,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer Joachim Hunold.  The new managers will start on May 1, the newspaper said
today in a preview of an article to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  